{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_07_03",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski043.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、はっ、はっ……！",
      "startTime": 1.9333331585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski044.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。どうでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 12.0666661501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……驚いた。キレが違うし、格段に凄みが出てる\nまるで別人じゃないか。一体何をしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 22.0781408232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの皆さんを直接尋ねて回ったんです\n曲やパフォーマンスにかける想いを聞こうと思って",
      "startTime": 30.1666669131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "三人に直接！？　よく話してくれたな",
      "startTime": 33.6928120138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、franさんとkanaさんには\n相手にもされませんでした",
      "startTime": 40.2333335798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんにも、初めは断られたんですが……粘りに\n粘って、ダンスを見てもらえることになったんです",
      "startTime": 46.9338951312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "といっても、教えてもらう約束をした訳ではなくて\n「勝手にやればいい」と言われただけなんですけどね",
      "startTime": 54.6333335798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 59.0296149495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、せっかくの機会ですから「遠慮せず、思った\nことはなんでも言って下さい！」と頼み込みました",
      "startTime": 64.8666664045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんに「それなら……厳しい言い方を\nするわね」と言われ、頷いたんです。そうしたら……",
      "startTime": 71.433330528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "第一声で「お遊戯会かと思った」と言われて……",
      "startTime": 77.4136495435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "「自分達の曲をこんな無様に踊られるなんてたまった\nものじゃない。曲の使用許可を取り下げたいくらい」",
      "startTime": 85.4999961774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "「半端な覚悟なら今すぐやめてほしい、曲を使われる\n私達まで迷惑だから」とまで言われました",
      "startTime": 94.2333295107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "正直心が折れそうでしたが、ここで怯んではお時間を\nいただいた意味がないので、アドバイスを求めました",
      "startTime": 102.7999961774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "「見てくれの振り付けだけは\n真似出来ているがそれだけ。上澄みしか見ていない」",
      "startTime": 108.066662844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 113.2007943079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "という言葉から始まって……アドバイスというよりは\nひたすら、容赦のないダメ出しを受け続けました",
      "startTime": 119.2999961774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "かなりハードな時間を過ごしたんだな……",
      "startTime": 122.9639516676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、大きな収穫が二つありました",
      "startTime": 126.3639516676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんの言葉は本当に容赦がなかったんですが\nどれも核心を突いていたんです",
      "startTime": 134.166662844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで、自分が向き合うべき課題を\nさらに具体的に深く知ることが出来ました",
      "startTime": 139.166654706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "月ストも皆包み隠さず声を掛け合っていたんですが……\nそれでも無意識のうちに遠慮していたのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 146.8999870221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……あまりにも厳しかったので、帰り道で\nちょっと泣いちゃったんですけどね",
      "startTime": 155.5333203554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよな。俺もmihoさんから厳しい言葉を\n掛けられることがあるから、気持ちはよく分かるよ",
      "startTime": 161.4435073622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "これが一つ目の収穫です。二つ目なんですが……",
      "startTime": 165.410188612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスがパフォーマンスにかける怖いくらいの\n覚悟や想い、そして誇りを感じ取ることが出来ました",
      "startTime": 173.6333305279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんと過ごした時間で分かったんです\n悩みの解決方法は意外とシンプルだったんだって",
      "startTime": 182.3294411949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "自分の課題と深く深く向き合って……\nあとは、覚悟を決める",
      "startTime": 190.2666628439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski023.m4a",
      "text": "これは別に、スリクスの皆さんのような才能がなくても\n出来ることなんだって気付きました",
      "startTime": 196.4666628439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "私の強みを生かして、自分なりのアプローチを続けて\n自分の課題と深く向き合って……想いを育てていきます",
      "startTime": 203.5043303454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "私だって、アイドルに対する覚悟や想いは\n誰よりも強い自信がありますから",
      "startTime": 212.6333284933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……短い間に、一気に成長したな\nこのまま、スリクスの曲で出場する方向でいいんだな？",
      "startTime": 220.3740095865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski026.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　楽しみにしていて下さいね",
      "startTime": 224.0406857501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ダンス大会当日",
      "startTime": 228.0666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.0999893188
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.0999893188
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.1792327574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski027.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ出番ですね",
      "startTime": 230.0792276711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "緊張は……程良くしてるみたいだな\nこれなら心配なさそうだ",
      "startTime": 236.9252248855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.0585555088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_07_03-ski028.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんですかね\nでも、今は確かに……なんだかうずうずしているんです",
      "startTime": 242.7999849874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
